[
  {
    "text": "Let's see,\nworks taking care of,",
    "start": 1.001,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Mr. Grouse is keeping an eye\non the house,",
    "start": 2.434,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Clyde and the McBrides\nare taking care",
    "start": 3.736,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "of Walt, Geo,\nCharles, and Cliff.",
    "start": 5.238,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": " ♪ Just a few more things and\n We'll all be relaxing in the--♪",
    "start": 7.139,
    "duration": 2.537
  },
  {
    "text": "[overlapping chatter]",
    "start": 9.809,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "...go horseback riding.",
    "start": 12.412,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "Why are you bringing that\non vacation?",
    "start": 13.78,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "You have your sun block,\nI have mine.",
    "start": 16.282,
    "duration": 2.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa, guys,\nthis is too much stuff!",
    "start": 18.551,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "Something's got to go back!",
    "start": 21.12,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "How 'bout this humungo bag?",
    "start": 22.521,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Absolutely not!\nThat one's very important!",
    "start": 24.624,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "- Puzzles?\n- The bag stays!",
    "start": 29.028,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "- Mine!\n- Mine too!",
    "start": 31.831,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "[whistling]",
    "start": 33.866,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Enough!\nStand back and let me work.",
    "start": 35.168,
    "duration": 2.569
  },
  {
    "text": "How did you do that?",
    "start": 38.871,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Quite simple, really.\nI merely used a formula",
    "start": 40.306,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "combining elements\nof spatial analysis,",
    "start": 42.609,
    "duration": 2.368
  },
  {
    "text": "and the basic physics theorem\nstating",
    "start": 45.111,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "that for every object-",
    "start": 46.879,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't ask\nif you don't really wanna know.",
    "start": 48.915,
    "duration": 2.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry kiddo,\nwe should get a move-on.",
    "start": 51.317,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "According to the reviews,",
    "start": 53.019,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "the hotel has\na very strict check-in policy.",
    "start": 54.487,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "If we're not there by eight,\nthey could give away our rooms!",
    "start": 56.189,
    "duration": 2.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait!\n[whistling]",
    "start": 59.358,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "[croaking]",
    "start": 61.661,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "[croaking]",
    "start": 65.565,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, here we go.\nLoud vacation time!",
    "start": 67.2,
    "duration": 3.469
  },
  {
    "text": "Can I get a 'What what?'",
    "start": 70.803,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "- What--\n- Wait! I forgot Lily's diapers!",
    "start": 72.138,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Turns out I also forgot Lily.",
    "start": 75.942,
    "duration": 1.634
  },
  {
    "text": "Poo-poo!",
    "start": 77.71,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": " ♪ We're going on vacation!\n We're going on vacation! ♪",
    "start": 79.378,
    "duration": 3.438
  },
  {
    "text": "[honking]",
    "start": 87.62,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't let\nthat old geezer pass us,",
    "start": 90.489,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad! Floor it!",
    "start": 92.759,
    "duration": 1.133
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it's- It is floored!",
    "start": 94.026,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "It's been floored\nthe whole time!",
    "start": 95.761,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "Dang show off in his hot rod.",
    "start": 97.931,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "Look! Come on, Dad!\nLet's get our dignity back!",
    "start": 101.133,
    "duration": 3.671
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm right there with ya, LJ.",
    "start": 105.004,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- Pass! Pass!\n- Father, this is not advisable!",
    "start": 106.639,
    "duration": 2.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Factoring in the angle\nof our descent,",
    "start": 109.475,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "current wind speed,\nand the condition",
    "start": 111.411,
    "duration": 1.634
  },
  {
    "text": "of this ageing heap, I fear",
    "start": 113.178,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "we are going to wind up...\n[screaming]",
    "start": 114.781,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "nose-first in a ditch.",
    "start": 117.449,
    "duration": 1.87
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping, crying]",
    "start": 119.485,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "My baby! What have I done?!",
    "start": 122.388,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Stand back and let me work.",
    "start": 124.59,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow! Nice job, sweetie.\nHow did you do that?",
    "start": 127.426,
    "duration": 3.304
  },
  {
    "text": "Eh, it was no biggie.",
    "start": 130.863,
    "duration": 1.269
  },
  {
    "text": "There was a crack\nin the cylinder block,",
    "start": 132.265,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "so I just re-routed\nthe exhaust manifold",
    "start": 133.666,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "past the carburetor, and then-",
    "start": 135.401,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't ask\nif you don't really wanna know.",
    "start": 137.737,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait! Okay, now we can go.",
    "start": 141.073,
    "duration": 3.438
  },
  {
    "text": "[honking]",
    "start": 144.644,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Dang it.",
    "start": 145.678,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, it's so hot.",
    "start": 148.681,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, can you turn on the AC\nbefore my hair totally frizzes?",
    "start": 150.583,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "[stalling]",
    "start": 154.02,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh. Doesn't seem to be working.",
    "start": 157.323,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh, the coolant must've leaked\nwhen we crashed.",
    "start": 158.825,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "Pull over, Pops.\nI'll check it out.",
    "start": 161.494,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "No can do. Remember,\neight o'clock check in.",
    "start": 162.928,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, can someone\njust roll down a window?",
    "start": 165.431,
    "duration": 2.402
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, honey, but if we roll\nany of these windows down,",
    "start": 167.967,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "they're not coming back up.",
    "start": 170.436,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "I know it's hot,",
    "start": 171.837,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "but just pretend\nyou're at the beach.",
    "start": 172.906,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "In this? Ugh, no!",
    "start": 175.107,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "[crunching]",
    "start": 177.376,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone want a low-cal bean chip?",
    "start": 179.678,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "- Vomit.\n- They're delicious,",
    "start": 181.614,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "and supes high fiber.\n[farting]",
    "start": 183.616,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, apparently.",
    "start": 185.851,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "It was the seat! See?",
    "start": 187.419,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "[groaning]",
    "start": 189.288,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Now it's not doing it.",
    "start": 190.422,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "Suffocating!",
    "start": 192.791,
    "duration": 1.436
  },
  {
    "text": "[coughing]\nAh!",
    "start": 194.36,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Be strong, kids! No windows!",
    "start": 196.295,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, agh, it's in my mouth!",
    "start": 198.431,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping]",
    "start": 201.834,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "- This is better!\n- What?!",
    "start": 203.869,
    "duration": 2.103
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 206.105,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Is everyone okay?",
    "start": 211.944,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "I've been better!",
    "start": 212.978,
    "duration": 1.703
  },
  {
    "text": "The good news is, the crash made\nthe windows go back up.",
    "start": 218.25,
    "duration": 3.037
  },
  {
    "text": "The bad news is,\nnow we have no door.",
    "start": 221.421,
    "duration": 2.168
  },
  {
    "text": "No way I can re-attach\nthis baby.",
    "start": 223.723,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "But I may have a solution.",
    "start": 227.526,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice fix, but we still have\na grave situation!",
    "start": 231.497,
    "duration": 3.304
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]\nGet it?",
    "start": 234.934,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "What? Don't set me up\nif you don't wanna hear a joke!",
    "start": 238.104,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait!",
    "start": 241.907,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 243.776,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Who's ready for lunch?",
    "start": 245.711,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- Me! Me! Me! Me!\n- I'm hungry!",
    "start": 247.347,
    "duration": 1.534
  },
  {
    "text": "Honey, let's start looking\nfor a good picnic stop.",
    "start": 249.014,
    "duration": 2.236
  },
  {
    "text": "No time! We're behind schedule.\nWe'll have to eat in the car.",
    "start": 251.383,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "I got this.\nSammies coming your way.",
    "start": 254.287,
    "duration": 2.435
  },
  {
    "text": "Think fast.",
    "start": 256.855,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Watch it!",
    "start": 258.424,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "Ow!",
    "start": 259.859,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Not so hard, dude!",
    "start": 261.159,
    "duration": 1.603
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't catch!",
    "start": 263.196,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "Those egg salad sandwiches were\ndelicious, honey.",
    "start": 266.565,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for making them.",
    "start": 269.635,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "You're totes welcome, Mom.",
    "start": 270.803,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Trash back here!",
    "start": 272.437,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "- Whoops.\n- Sorry.",
    "start": 274.34,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "- I can't throw, either.\n- Weak.",
    "start": 275.875,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "[growling]",
    "start": 278.21,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa, guys, you feeling alright?\nI'm not feeling too good myself.",
    "start": 280.379,
    "duration": 5.106
  },
  {
    "text": "Leni, what exactly\ndid you put in those sandwiches?",
    "start": 286.819,
    "duration": 3.637
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't remember.\nI made them weeks ago.",
    "start": 290.723,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "- Leni!\n- What?",
    "start": 293.058,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "That can't be good.",
    "start": 294.727,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I was so excited\nfor the trip,",
    "start": 296.395,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "I wanted to get a head start!",
    "start": 297.797,
    "duration": 1.567
  },
  {
    "text": "[siblings groaning]",
    "start": 299.498,
    "duration": 2.737
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-oh. I think I'm gonna barf!",
    "start": 302.602,
    "duration": 1.834
  },
  {
    "text": "I second that!",
    "start": 304.57,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Puke fest!",
    "start": 306.005,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "Pull over, Dad!",
    "start": 307.272,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "No time! Use a bag!",
    "start": 308.374,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "- Lynn!\n- Okay! Okay!",
    "start": 309.708,
    "duration": 2.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my gosh!",
    "start": 314.313,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an emergency!\n[toilets flushing]",
    "start": 316.449,
    "duration": 2.769
  },
  {
    "text": "Leni, you're off lunch duty\nuntil further notice.",
    "start": 319.919,
    "duration": 3.503
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, let's just round that up\nto 'forever'.",
    "start": 323.556,
    "duration": 3.103
  }
]